text: Paweł Tarło (died 1565) was a Polish noble. Tarło was canon of Kraków, dean of Przemyśl and Archbishop of Lwów from 1561. Category:16th-century births Category:1565 deaths Category:16th-century Roman Catholic archbishops Pawel Category:Archbishops of Lviv Category:Canons of Kraków
title: Paweł Tarło
